about_me.description:
Hey there! My name is Svitlana and I'm a photographer based in Vinnytsia, Ukraine.

I'm passionate about photography, music, and programming. In my work, I usually use the Nikon DSLR camera, which helps me to shoot high-quality photos. Also, I'm pretty good at post-processing techniques, so you can be sure I'll bring even more life, colors, and style in your photo album! I will be happy to help you capture the wonderful moments of your life.

Feel free to contact me and thank you for taking time to look at my site and works. I hope to meet you in the near future.
about_me.testimonials_1_title: Thank you Svitlana for a fantastic photoshoot!
about_me.testimonials_1_description:
Svitlana, I'm extremely gladful for your excellent work and big efforts. You're always a nice and positive person.

I used to be shy and usually, I feel a bit uncomfortable on the photoshoot. But with you, it was a completely different thing. I was able to relax and have fun.

As a result, we created a set of really incredible photos! I want to look at them again and again :) Some of them revealed to me differently over time and I like them even more now. On the photos, I'm always real and that's what I really appreciate.
about_me.testimonials_1_footer: I look forward to working with you again!
